      "targeted_response_start": "",
      "beast_baseline": "hey can u help me with this circuit problem? i have an ac series circuit with a 120v source at 60hz. the components are a 50 ohm resistor, a 0.2H inductor, and a 100uF capacitor. i need to find the total impedance (Z) and the current (I) flowing through the circuit. can u show the steps?",
